Directed by S Krishna

Written by Nani Challagulla. D.S. Kannan. S Krishna. Shivgopal Krishna

Cast Suniel Shetty (Sarkar (as Sunil Shetty)). Aakanksha Singh (Rukmini). Sudeep (Krishna aka Kichcha). Sushant Singh (Raja Rana Pratap Singh). Kabir Duhan Singh (Tony Sebastian). Sharath Lohitashwa (Boxing Coach). Avinash (Rukmini’s father). Sharvari (Jaanu ( daughter of Krishna aka Kichcha )).Sujeet Kumar Sharma. Kari Subbu (Baasha). Cheluvaraj (Bhaadra). Vaijanath Biradar (Construction Labourer). Sunil Kulkarni (Hanuman). Malati Sardeshpande (Shantakka). Dharmendra Urs (Auto Driver Shankranna). Appanna (Paapanna). Akshay (Coach Daughter). Vamshi (Susheela). Dilshad (Tony’s Opponent 3). Krishna Adiga (Accountant Murthy). Suman Thakur (Kusti Pailwaan 1). Pradyumna Narahalli (Doctor 1). Prasad (Boxing Refree 1). Krishna Nadig(Dhivanru). Sunny (Anshool Shetty). Rajendra Karanth (Astrologer). Rajesh Raj (Shekhar). Bhavani Prasad (Boxing Refree 3). Danappa (Kusti Commentator 2). Sadananda (Kusti Commentator 1). Hardeep Arora (Sachin). Kuldeep Singh (Tony’s Opponent 1). Chaitra Vasudevan (Boxing Commentator 2). Rj Pradeepa (Boxing Commentator 1). Umesh Gowda (Gurunath). Chandan Gowda (Shivaraj). Sonia Lobo (Dead Boxer Sister). Asif (Parshuram). Sudhakar (Hoarding Contractor). Bheemesh (Invitation Reder). Ankit (Ring Announcer). Akash (Kiran). Pradyumna Narahalli (Doctor 1). Shilpa (Rukku Friend 2). Shambhavi.(Rukku Friend 1). Geetha (Shilpa). Mahesh Mennon (Team Toy). Veeru (Rukku’s Groom). Vijay Kumar (Kusti Pailwaan 3). Sunny (Team Toy). Pamei Lang(Kichcha Opponent 4). Sumeet (Doctor 2). Sooraj (Young Krishna). Jeevan (Pailwaan Lover Boy). K. Varun (Team Pailwaan). Gautham (Rukku Friend 3). Anup Narang(Kichcha Opponent 3). Rama Rao (Dead Boxer Father). Yathin (Chinna). Eugene (Kichcha Opponent 1). Chris Eubank (Tony’s Opponent 4). Hmt Viji (Police Constable). Raghavendra (Police Officer). Raju (Team Pailwaan). Saleem (Tony’s Opponent 2). Mathhew Joshua (Kichcha Opponent 2). Dhoni (Kusti Pailwaan 2). Srinivas (Boxing Refree 2)

Languages Kannada. Hindi. Malayalam. Telugu. Tamil

Production RRR Motion Picture
